&bull; <b> 	Stay safe online: </b> If the bullying or harassment is happening online, take steps to protect yourself. Block or unfriend the person involved, adjust your privacy settings, and consider reporting the behavior to the platform or website administrators. Limit your exposure to online platforms where the harassment is occurring if necessary.<br><br>
